12. when catkin build kalibr_workspace 
    P : catkin:command not found
    S : sudo apt-get install ros-melodic-catkin python-catkin-tools 


13. when catkin build kalibr_workspace have error in process
      S :
      ## install dependency package
      sudo apt-get install python-setuptools python-rosinstall ipython libeigen3-dev libboost-all-dev doxygen libopencv-dev ros-melodic-vision-opencv ros-melodic-image-transport-plugins ros-melodic-cmake-modules software-properties-common software-properties-common libpoco-dev python-matplotlib python-scipy python-git python-pip ipython libtbb-dev libblas-dev liblapack-dev python-catkin-tools libv4l-dev
      sudo apt-get update
      sudo apt-get upgrade
      ## rebuild a new workspace 
      mkdir -p ~/kalibr_workspace/src
      cd ~/kalibr_workspace
      source /opt/ros/melodic/setup.bash
      catkin init
      catkin config --extend /opt/ros/melodic
      catkin config --merge-devel
      cd ~/kalibr_workspace/src
      git clone https://github.com/ethz-asl/Kalibr.git
      cd ~/kalibr_workspace
      catkin build -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release -j4

14. when catkin build kalibr_workspace have CMake version error
      P : error: ISO C++17 does not allow dynamic exception specifications
      S : g++ verison is not allow verison 11
      sudo update-alternatives --remove-all g++
      sudo update-alternatives --install /usr/bin/g++ g++ /usr/bin/g++-7 1

15. when use kalibr_create_target_pdf to make Aprilgrid
      P : No module named pyx
      S : install pyx
      pip install pyx
      or 
      pip install PyX==0.12

16. when use kalibr_create_target_pdf make an apriltag
      P : IOError: [Errno 32] Broken pipe
      S : install python-pyx instead of pyx
      sudo apt install python-pyx
      
17. when rosrun kalibr_calibrate_cameras
